#include <iostream>
#include <string>
using namespace std;
int main() {
	int t;
	cin>>t;
	for(int i=0;i<t;++i) {
		string s;
		cin>>s;
		int flag=0;
		for(int i=0;i<s.size();++i) {
			if(s[i]=='a' || s[i]=='e' || s[i]=='i' || s[i]=='o' || s[i]=='u')
			flag=1;
		}
		if(flag==1)
		cout<<"Neha wins"<<endl;
		else
		cout<<"Shilpa wins"<<endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
